{"tid":1679264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"催淚彈昨日射入油麻地一藥房　警方今早派人到藥房致歉","createTime":"2019-10-28T06:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T07:23:17.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1935715b524442e913db4549a8bf349d1806dd","tid":1679264,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:12:00.000Z","msg":"昨日警方在油尖旺一帶施放多輪催淚彈驅散示威者，其中有催淚彈射入油麻地一間藥房，警方今早派人到藥房致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>藥房負責人胡先生說，早上11時許有4名警方代表，到藥房表示「唔好意思」，希望藥房體諒，警方代表逗留約2分鐘後離開，他們無解釋催淚彈射入藥房的原因。胡先生說，無辦法下唯有接受道歉。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>藥房仍點算損失金額，胡先生說，暫時有6樽保健產品受催淚彈影響，包裝燒焦，損失約1000元</strong>，待藥房老闆回港，才決定會否追究。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488608-20191028.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488608-20191028.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5wHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=867a45a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488608-20191028.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ba1ee44d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488608-20191028.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7ec9844fbcac6c86c8ce32975442b7a9b87eeb05","tid":1679264,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9b76f9f1f6c1a2a3a67120fe870021e12c6af457","tid":1679264,"uid":286131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />道歉有用？d藥自己食返"},{"pid":"a9fc5d88fc8b2921a7b1775860f13d1bc83492ea","t